text: 80/20 or 80-20 may refer to: * 80/20 housing, housing of which 20% is "affordable", encouraged by regulation in the U.S. * 80-20 rule or the Pareto principle * 80-20 Initiative, an Asian American political organization * 80/20 Thinking, a UK Privacy consultancy firm * T-slot structural framing, a framing system sometimes known as "80/20 framing" after one manufacturer
